          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DIFFR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Starting  from  the  high-energy  end  of  an",
                " experimental spectrum,  which contain transitions to",
                " the ground state only,  the simulated intensities of",
                " the  transitions  to  the  ground state (Monte Carlo",
                " procedure) were normalized to the experimental  once",
                " and the  intensity  distribution  of  the  branching",
                " transitions was  subtracted  from  the  experimental",
                " spectrum. Dividing    the    intensities    of   the",
                " transitions to   the   ground   state,   which   are",
                " proportional to    the    elastic-scattering   cross",
                " sections by    corresponding    branching    ratios,",
                " specially measured,  photoabsorption  cross  section",
                " was obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
